## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **semaglutide 2.4mg Wegovy 2021** = first weekly GLP-1 obesity FDA. STEP-1 ~15% TBWL = behavior + lifestyle 시대 종료, 약리 시대 시작. quantum-VQE 의 GLP-1R class B GPCR scaffold direct fit.
2. **tirzepatide Zepbound 2023** = GIP+GLP-1 dual agonist. SURMOUNT-1 ~22% TBWL = GLP-1 mono 보다 ~7%p 우월. quantum-VQE 의 dual receptor PPI orchestration.
3. **retatrutide research 2023 Phase 2 ~24% TBWL** = GIP+GLP-1+glucagon triple agonist. GCGR 추가 = energy expenditure + lipolysis 추가 mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 triple-receptor selectivity refinement = hxq-ob-triple-001 candidate 의 직접 fit.
4. **setmelanotide Imcivree 2020 → 2022 BBS** = first FDA MC4R agonist for POMC/LEPR + 2022 Bardet-Biedl 확대. 단일유전자성 비만 paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 MC4R (class A GPCR) allosteric vs orthosteric.
5. **semaglutide SELECT 2023** = first CV mortality benefit weight-loss drug (8% relative reduction). FDA 2024 Medicare CV indication 확대. obesity drug 가 lifestyle 약 → CV 약 전환 paradigm.
6. **semaglutide STEP-TEENS 2022** = 12+ adolescent 확대. 소아청소년 비만 약리 paradigm shift (cross-adolescent).
7. **cagrilintide + semaglutide CagriSema research** = amylin + GLP-1 dual fixed-ratio. 다른 receptor class 조합. quantum-VQE 의 amylin receptor (calcitonin family) + class B GPCR 조합 selectivity.
8. **monlunabant CB1 peripheral-selective Lilly research** = rimonabant 2008 withdrawal (psych SE) lessons → 말초 한정. quantum-VQE 의 CB1 BBB exclusion scaffold.
9. **naltrexone-bupropion Contrave 2014 + phentermine-topiramate Qsymia 2012 + orlistat 1999** = pre-GLP-1 era 약리. modest TBWL ~5-10%. GLP-1 era 가 paradigm shift = pre-2021 vs post-2021 명확.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, obesity 임상 의미 한정. compounding pharmacy 2023-24 shortage quality concerns + Medicare/Medicaid coverage 한정 = access ethics 임상-orthogonal.

